供資料，佢曾經拍拖3次，係2019年2月正式就任警察時，迅即同一名同區警察發展關係。<br />\n<br />\n係2019年6月示威開始之後，佢多次表示好愛警察呢一份工，又鬧示威者搞事，如果有機會係鎮壓現場就會盡全力毆打示威者。"},{"pid":"7244fe68cf7a65e66e54ced007c1231b8cbddb29","tid":1724182,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:44:24.000Z","msg":"我相信你地"},{"pid":"1b351b08de47149bfbc349e9ecf953cac16954ca","tid":1724182,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T11:44:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YndTzsZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYndTzsZ.jpg&h=2766aa75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/us2X070.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fus2X070.jpg&h=a14d911e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你要攬炒, 就唔好聽左膠, 有底線不燒民居/人不犯我我不犯人就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不嬲都話有人扮極端主義係咁吹風<br />\n冇手足做呢o的極端野啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過巴打你個POST有樣好, 下面成批打手現型跟風<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n上次已經檢討啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提完一次再開一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小事化大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">邊個再開POST就是左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8decbbe591f52ec12a59c9c9051204063ae4df00","tid":1724182,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T1